data.description: Check out this super functional 3-bedroom home in the Sprague school district of South Salem! The 1,504 SQFT house has two separate living areas, a fireplace, a dedicated laundry room, and a remodeled kitchen! Just minutes from Sumpter City Park and quick access to Kuebler Blvd, this home is well-located in an attractive neighborhood. A low-maintenance yard is fully fenced in the back, plus a beautiful cherry tree in the front. All this and a two-car garage make this place feel like home! Co-Agent related to Seller.
